title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 04.28.30
description:
IS HE A MOLESTER?

A chilling allegation? Alex has been accused of some of the most heinous molestation charges Steve&#039;s ever heard. His ex-wife, Kaila, first launched the investigation after their 5-year-old daughter made an alarming confession. Alex&#039;s sister, Leslie, says that she heard her own confession from Kaila, admitting she made the entire story up to get back at Alex. This story is no joke, and Steve&#039;s going to find the truth behind it all.
